25|$|The {{urgent need}} to address climate change {{was one of the}} primary factors {{motivating}} Lessig to run for president. He supports <b>a</b> <b>carbon</b> <b>tax</b> on companies that are not able to clean the pollution that they have created. He also supports the other policies Democratic presidential candidates have proposed, but he argues that <b>a</b> <b>carbon</b> <b>tax</b> would render most of them unnecessary. He also argues that enacting the Citizen Equality Act is essential to make addressing climate change possible because fossil fuel interests are currently using their unequal influence to block it.|$|E
